{#
name: Health Check Monitor
description: Monitor system health and alert on issues
tags: [monitoring, health, alert, endpoint]
parameters:
  - name: skill_name
    type: str
    description: Skill display name
    required: true
  - name: skill_description
    type: str
    description: Brief description of what this monitor does
    required: true
  - name: check_interval
    type: int
    description: Check interval in seconds
    default: 60
  - name: alert_threshold
    type: int
    description: Failed checks before alerting
    default: 3
  - name: endpoints
    type: str
    description: Comma-separated list of endpoints to check
    required: true
examples:
  - "Health check for API endpoints every 60 seconds"
  - "Monitor /health, /ready every 30 seconds"
#}
---
name: {{ skill_name | kebab_case }}
description: {{ skill_description }}
metadata:
  author: owlclaw
  version: "1.0"
owlclaw:
  spec_version: "1.0"
  task_type: monitoring
  constraints:
    max_daily_calls: 1440
---
# {{ skill_name }} — 使用指南

## 目标

{{ skill_description }}

## 检查项

- 检查以下端点可用性：{{ endpoints }}
- 检查间隔：{{ check_interval }} 秒
- 连续失败 {{ alert_threshold }} 次后触发告警

## 告警策略

- 端点无响应或返回非 2xx 时记录失败
- 达到阈值后执行告警流程

## 注意事项

- 确保 endpoints 格式正确（逗号分隔）
- 建议 check_interval 不少于 30 秒，避免过于频繁
